个人简介
			
			JianQiShenwasborninHangzhou,ChinaonNovember30,1974.HereceivedtheB.Sc.degreeintheoreticalphysicsfromNanjingUniversity,Chinain1999,andreceivedtheMasterdegreefromthedepartmentofphysicsofZhejiangUniversityin2002.Hehasbeenengagedinquantumopticsandelectromagnetismsince2002,andreceivedthejointPhDfromtheRoyalSwedishInstituteofTechnology(KTH)andZhejiangUniversity(opticsinZhejiangUniversityandtheoreticalelectromagnetisminKTH).JianQiShenhaspublishedover100researchpapersandbookchaptersintheareasofoptics,artificialelectromagneticmaterials,quantumtheoryandgravitation,inwhichhehasstudiedthetopicssuchasquantum-vacuumgeometricphases,quantum-coherentnegativerefraction,dynamicsoftopologicaldualmass,massspectraofleptonsaswellasspin-connectiongravitationalgaugefieldtheory.Duringthepastfouryears,hehasbeensupportedfinanciallybythePostdoctoralFoundationsandtheNationalNaturalScienceFoundationsofChina.Hepublishedareviewbookentitled&quot;Quantum&amp;ClassicalOpticalPropertiesofArtificialElectromagneticMedia&quot;(ISBN:978-81-7895-356-4,TransworldResearchNetwork,India,2008).Since2008,heisanassociateprofessorofZhejiangUniversity.
			
				
			工作研究领域
			
			Optics,artificialelectromagneticmaterials,quantumtheoryandgravitation
			
				
